metadata.title: Seabird Colony Locations
metadata.description: Data Type: Birds;  1989 Seabird Colony Catalog data for the oil spill affected area were converted to an ARC/INFO format. Contains colony locations only. No attribute data (species, colony size, etc.) is included.
